You haven't been to the main guild in the city of
Rein Garnet, have you? First, please talk to the
guild leader there.

And if you don't join the guild, you won't be able
to do any quests or anything else at this branch
guild.

Welcome, magical girls. This is the Traveling
Guild. How may I assist you?

If you have any questions or concerns, feel free
to ask.
この村のリーダーについて

The leader of this succubus village is a loli
demon named \C[2]Louisa\C[0]. She has a gentle
personality and seems to be admired by everyone.

However, it seems that she is quite promiscuous
and constantly seeks men in terms of sexuality.
Since there are fewer men around, she seems to be
a bit frustrated and irritated.
起きている問題について

It seems that the succubus treasure has been
stolen by someone. It appears that Louisa's power
has weakened, doesn't it?

As a result, the demons have become more active,
causing a shortage of semen supply to the village.
It seems that the entire village is struggling
with a shortage of sperm.
First, it would be good to talk to Louisa.

Oh? Why are you naked? Did you receive a repair
kit?

By the way, I heard there was a pretty big attack
in the town. It seems like the barrier pillars
were destroyed. It's quite terrifying, isn't it?

Could you stop right here for a moment? Everyone
is here to work seriously, you know.

Quests can be quite tough, you know. Once you
accept one, you have to do it properly and can't
afford to lose... I can understand the feeling of
wanting to drop out.

What? Do you think you've become a succubus or
something? How troublesome.

I understand that there might be a shortage of
semen, but it seems like it's going a bit too far.
In fact, there are men who have come close to
dying because of it.

If you're going to meet the leader, at least put
on some clothes.

The leader of this village is Lady Louisa. I
request that you behave properly, magical girls.

What's the point of tempting us? We're only
interested in cum.
ここでアイテムゲット
攻撃手段を持つ相手であれば戦闘へ
そうでなければ、相手は一方的にダメージを受ける。
二回目で殺してしまう
元いた場所に戻るように
Hey! You there! Your crimes have been revealed!
Do you think you can defeat me?en(v[263]>=100)
\C[3]☠私に勝てるとでも思ってる？en(v[263]>=100)
You're giving me a hard time, damn it.

Mm, did you get taken down by the demon? Be
careful.

I'm in trouble. My fiancée, Lumie, is in the town
of Rein, but when I send letters, they don't reach
her and they come back.

I occasionally send money, although it's not much,
and there haven't been any issues on your end. I'm
pretty sure Lumie is in Rein without a doubt...

It's bothering me, but I'm swamped with work
quests and can't find the time to go see her. If
it's alright with you, could you search for her
and deliver a letter if you find her?

Alright, I often return to town so there shouldn't
be any issues. I wonder where she is? Lumie is...

My house is in the residential area of Rein, the
house with the blue roof. There are some issues in
my family... so maybe she's not there...

The house with the blue roof in the residential
area... Hmm, got it. I'll go check it out for now,
and if she's not there, I'll try to search for
her.

Thank you, I appreciate it. Once you deliver the
letter, please let me know.
I'm busy right now, so let's talk later, okay?

Mm, did you get taken down by the demon? Be
careful.

My house is in the residential area of Rein, the
Blue Roof House. There are some issues in my
family... so maybe she might not be there...

Mm, did you get taken down by the demon? Be
careful.
Thank you! Did Rudia say anything?

It seems like she was right in the middle of work.
But I made sure to deliver it to her properly, so
there shouldn't be any problem.

Work? Hmm... I'm still struggling with money... I
need to work harder...

But Konoha, I was relieved to know that my fiance
is safe. Thank you!
Yes... (I can't really say the truth...)
※ルゥミィからローレンに手紙が届いて、真相は
言わないままなので、ローレンは何も知らずのまま
ルゥミィから手紙が来ないので不審に思ったローレンは
仕事を片付け、リインに戻り……

Mm, did you get taken down by the demon? Be
careful.

Thank you for that time. Thanks to you, my work is
going smoothly.
